reviews.text: The food just eatable! Don't expect too much! It is busy always in rush hour and you need too wait and sit with others in a small place!
Well above expectations: location, cleaniness, tasty food & drinks & services. Sure will make visits again for all
Food is fresh and price is acceptable.

Disgusting! Bad, not recommended!
i usually never rate a bad restaurant, but this restaurant is really bad and i feel like its my call to warn customers in advance to not get the same experience as what i went through. there was no waiting line so we could dine in and order immediately. While we waited for our meal a Giant cockroach flew or fell from the ceiling on my hand! Scared the hell outta me, staff came to me and found the cockroach and killed it. I know cockroaches are not harmful, but its just really disgusting as it was as big as my thumb! Then I got my lemon tea and i drunk all of it then i removed the three slices of lemon with my spoon and i did a shocking discovery. At the bottom there was some leftovers rice (one spoonful), so i asked the staff how this got in my cup. The staff couldn't give me an answer and there was only a few options in my head 1. they did not wash the cup and served the lemon tea to me in a dirty cup with leftover rice from customers or 2. they put leftover rice from customers on purpose in my cup.How can you not know that the cup is dirty with rice you have to pour hot water in it and 3 slices of lemon........just Disgusting that I drank all of it!! i almost puked thinking about it urghhhh Bleh! I of course informed the staff about this but they just waved my complaint away and didn't even apologise to me neither was the lemon tea deducted from the bill and i had to pay the full price. They told me that i should have told them earlier so that they can serve me a new one, but even if they serve me a new one i rather not drink at all and how can i inform them earlier when the leftover rice is at the bottom and hidden under the slices of lemon??? YUCK! This should not be like this in the first place!
Sorry, but never this restaurant in Yuen long for me again! just too DISGUSTING and Terrible staff!
Very Friendly, good service, focus on 街坊鄰居。food portion is big and delicious.

result.name: 利興餐廳

reviews.text:
服務好過其他餐廳，價錢彼此大約相似，起碼唔似：凰X，有大老🐭，仲走嚟走去，好似餐廳寵物，而老闆仲話啲客好似睇慣，唔怕，真荒謬。
但如果在教X路利興進食，它可以提供許多不潔嘅碗筷黏滿上手食過嘅痕跡，湯裏都可以能找到一些驚喜，而晚間嗰收錢啊姐，會好肯定話比你/你們知，小小污漬梗有架，真精彩嘅餐廳。

食物水準及服務，非常一般。

不知是否雨天關係，晚上九点左右已经很少顧客，適合聊天。
錯，坐得舒適，有很多美食可供選擇，值得推介
一碗簡單嘅麵 出前一丁 都煮唔好 好難生存啦
食物不錯。員工友善。服務態度 ~ 好。 👍🏻😊
